the Church would fall apart.

23:50.179 --> 23:51.215
OLMA: Thank you.

23:51.305 --> 23:53.843
FATHER MICHAEL:
God will reward you.

23:54.183 --> 23:56.300
I appreciate what you're
doing here, John.

23:56.393 --> 23:58.134
JULLIARD: Thank you, Father.
I appreciate that very much.

23:58.229 --> 23:59.229
RAPHAEL: João Clemente.

24:00.231 --> 24:01.642
GARDO: João Clemente.

24:01.938 --> 24:03.418
Safe journey, Father.
(GARDO SPEAKING)

24:03.442 --> 24:04.649
The internet is slow.

24:05.027 --> 24:07.147
FATHER MICHAEL: Get yourself
an air conditioner, John.

24:07.154 --> 24:08.395
So many links.

24:09.365 --> 24:10.365
(CLICKING)

24:10.533 --> 24:12.365
He was a lawyer.

24:12.910 --> 24:14.867
(CAR ENGINE STARTING)
OLMA: How did it go?

24:15.037 --> 24:16.037
JULLIARD: Terrible.

24:16.205 --> 24:17.446
If it wasn't for the check,

24:17.540 --> 24:19.540
I would have strangled
the self-righteous hypocrite

24:19.625 --> 24:20.866
before he walked out the door.

24:21.001 --> 24:22.001
(SIGHING)

24:22.378 --> 24:23.378
He needs a drink.

24:23.712 --> 24:25.624
(SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)
Where did you come from?

24:25.714 --> 24:26.921
He needs a drink.

24:27.133 --> 24:28.544
He needs a drink? Yeah.

24:28.717 --> 24:30.845
Yeah, he does. Let's go.

24:31.554 --> 24:32.635
Okay.

24:34.431 --> 24:36.423
Hurry, hurry!

24:38.144 --> 24:40.101
(SIGHING) It couldn't
have been that bad.

24:40.187 --> 24:42.053
I mean, it's not like
they're firing you.

24:42.148 --> 24:44.515
No, honey, he couldn't fire me,

24:44.733 --> 24:46.395
but he was threatening
to reassign me.

24:47.653 --> 24:49.519
Gabriel, are you hungry?

24:49.613 --> 24:50.613
<i>Sim.</i>

24:50.781 --> 24:52.568
Activist - what's that?

24:52.658 --> 24:53.658
(GARDO SPEAKING)

24:53.742 --> 24:55.182
He built lots of houses
for the poor.

24:55.202 --> 24:56.864
Do you like ham and cheese? <i>Sim.</i>

24:57.037 --> 24:58.949
(SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)
Tomato, yes.

24:59.248 --> 25:01.114
Slice that up, will you?

25:01.584 --> 25:03.621
They stopped him.

25:03.752 --> 25:04.788
OLMA: Why would
they reassign you?

25:04.879 --> 25:06.120
FATHER MICHAEL: To silence me.

25:06.213 --> 25:08.546
It means, wherever there is corruption,
wherever there is injustice,

25:08.716 --> 25:10.082
wherever there is
police brutality,

25:10.593 --> 25:12.425
I must keep my eyes
closed, shut my mouth,

25:12.511 --> 25:14.343
and say my prayers. <i>Voilà.</i>

25:14.680 --> 25:17.263
(SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)

25:21.103 --> 25:22.184
(RAPHAEL SPEAKING)

25:22.271 --> 25:23.271
Look at that.

25:25.191 --> 25:26.648
He took to the streets.

25:27.651 --> 25:28.651
More butter.

25:29.195 --> 25:30.902
The ungrateful little bastard.

25:30.988 --> 25:32.320
"Bas"? "Bas"?

25:32.615 --> 25:34.106
Then they put him in jail.

25:34.700 --> 25:35.941
Something's not right.

25:38.829 --> 25:40.411
Here. You remake the sandwich.

25:40.706 --> 25:42.586
I gotta get down to the
bank and cash that check

25:42.625 --> 25:46.118
in case His Holiness decides to
cancel it before he leaves town.

25:46.295 --> 25:47.706
I'll see you later. Thank you.

25:48.339 --> 25:49.955
(SPEAKING PORTUGUESE) What now?

25:50.132 --> 25:51.132
Print! Print!

25:51.342 --> 25:52.378
What now?

25:53.177 --> 25:54.293
Bless me.

25:55.137 --> 25:57.129
(SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)

26:01.268 --> 26:02.268
Amen.

26:04.063 --> 26:05.224
(RATO WHISTLING)

26:07.483 --> 26:08.483
Butter?

26:08.567 --> 26:09.567
<i>Sim.</i>

26:09.818 --> 26:10.818
Lettuce?

26:10.819 --> 26:11.819
<i>Sim.</i>

26:13.155 --> 26:14.191
More cheese?

26:17.910 --> 26:20.152
(INDISTINCT CHATTER)

26:26.794 --> 26:28.660
I found it! I found it!

26:29.421 --> 26:30.707
(MAN SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)

26:36.345 --> 26:37.345
(SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)

26:37.721 --> 26:40.054
No - back to work, punk.

26:43.435 --> 26:44.687
(FREDERICO SPEAKING)

26:44.770 --> 26:47.387
Boy! Come here.

26:51.026 --> 26:52.026
Everyone here?

26:52.111 --> 26:53.147
Yes.

26:54.363 --> 26:57.856
Do you know those boys, Raphael
and Gardo - they here?

27:05.040 --> 27:07.418
They didn't come to work today.

27:09.211 --> 27:10.418
(SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)

27:12.099 --> 27:13.900
(VIDEOGAME BEEPING)
(RATO SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)

27:13.924 --> 27:16.507
So, the guy in prison
is a serial killer.

27:16.593 --> 27:20.132
And José Angelo
buries the bodies.

27:20.222 --> 27:21.222
(GARDO CHUCKLING)

27:21.390 --> 27:24.258
None of that's written there.

27:24.768 --> 27:26.430
You can't even read!

27:26.603 --> 27:29.016
Pay me two bucks
for playing my game.

27:29.106 --> 27:30.106
(GASPS) Pfft!

27:30.941 --> 27:32.728
He thinks I'm paying for it!

27:32.860 --> 27:34.067
(LAUGHING)

27:34.945 --> 27:37.062
This game is sick.

27:37.156 --> 27:38.021
Want to buy it?

27:38.115 --> 27:39.115
How much?

27:39.491 --> 27:40.491
R$800.

27:40.617 --> 27:41.698
(SCOFFS)

27:42.244 --> 27:43.780
(SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)

27:45.080 --> 27:47.993
Give the wallet back
and we can buy the game.

27:49.585 --> 27:51.292
Let me think about it.

27:51.962 --> 27:52.998
(GARDO SPEAKING)

27:53.088 --> 27:55.045
Seriously, let's get
that reward.

27:55.132 --> 27:56.132
Not yet.

27:56.759 --> 27:58.170
Let's talk
to the prisoner first.

27:58.260 --> 27:59.762
Not me.

28:00.596 --> 28:02.258
I'll go on my own then.

28:05.059 --> 28:06.721
(BEEPING) Hey, Raphael.

28:07.478 --> 28:09.344
Forget the guy in jail.

28:09.938 --> 28:12.021
We give Rat R$500...

28:12.608 --> 28:14.019
He'll take it.

28:15.110 --> 28:16.772
The game's not worth more.

28:18.113 --> 28:19.615
We rent it...

28:19.698 --> 28:22.691
50 cents for 30 minutes.

28:23.535 --> 28:25.276
(GARDO SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)
RAPHAEL: Gardo!

28:25.496 --> 28:27.533
Look, I'm about to win!

28:30.276 --> 28:31.436
Piece of shit - it's crashed.

28:31.460 --> 28:32.792
(VIDEOGAME BEEPING)

28:33.379 --> 28:35.120
Gardo! Gardo!
(SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)

28:38.008 --> 28:39.008
Raphael!

28:39.885 --> 28:40.885
Gardo!

28:41.470 --> 28:43.427
Raphael! Raphael!

28:45.557 --> 28:47.014
You think he can help?

28:47.184 --> 28:48.641
He's a priest!

28:49.937 --> 28:51.849
(BELL CLANGING)
(SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)

28:52.856 --> 28:54.392
You can't wake him up!

28:54.566 --> 28:55.566
(SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)

28:56.527 --> 28:57.563
Wait here.

29:02.032 --> 29:03.068
GARDO: Father Julliard!

29:03.575 --> 29:04.827
Wake up.

29:04.904 --> 29:06.304
Father Julliard!
(JULLIARD GROANING)

29:06.328 --> 29:07.364
(GARDO SPEAKING)

29:07.454 --> 29:08.535
Raphael's been taken.

29:13.377 --> 29:14.663
(RAPHAEL SHOUTING IN PORTUGUESE)

29:16.255 --> 29:17.336
(RAPHAEL GRUNTING)

29:22.302 --> 29:23.338
(SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)

29:23.804 --> 29:24.920
(GRUNTING)

29:34.565 --> 29:37.399
You should've
taken me seriously.

29:38.152 --> 29:39.152
(RAPHAEL GRUNTING)

29:47.995 --> 29:49.111
(CAR DOOR CLOSING)

29:53.459 --> 29:54.459
(SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)

29:55.544 --> 29:56.751
Have you had dinner?

29:57.588 --> 30:00.251
I don't want you
messing up the car.

30:05.179 --> 30:06.215
(TIRES SQUEALING)

30:06.388 --> 30:07.799
(SLAMMING) (GASPS)

30:16.648 --> 30:18.355
(CLASSICAL MUSIC PLAYING)

30:25.407 --> 30:26.407
(GRUNTING)

30:30.787 --> 30:31.787
(GRUNTING)

30:33.790 --> 30:34.871
(YELLING) (SLAMMING)

30:40.506 --> 30:41.713
(GROANING)

30:44.092 --> 30:45.092
(CLANGING)

30:48.347 --> 30:49.428
(GRUNTING)

31:09.451 --> 31:10.692
(SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)

31:13.997 --> 31:15.078
(GRUNTING)

31:18.126 --> 31:19.287
(CELL PHONE BEEPING)

31:19.378 --> 31:20.459
(SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)

31:21.129 --> 31:24.042
I'm looking for a boy.

31:24.132 --> 31:27.296
Raphael Fernandes.
Here's a photo.

31:27.386 --> 31:28.386
(MAN SPEAKING)

31:28.470 --> 31:29.631
We don't take minors here.

31:29.721 --> 31:31.713
I know he's here.

31:31.807 --> 31:33.168
(MAN SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)
<i>Sim, sim.</i>

31:33.225 --> 31:34.225
(MAN SPEAKING)

31:34.309 --> 31:36.301
No minors in here -
this is a police station.

31:47.823 --> 31:48.823
RAPHAEL: Ahhh!

31:49.074 --> 31:50.815
(RAPHAEL SOBBING)

31:58.458 --> 32:00.541
(PANTING)

32:06.008 --> 32:07.044
Water?

32:19.563 --> 32:20.599
(GRUNTING)

32:24.359 --> 32:25.520
I found...

32:26.612 --> 32:28.228
R$300.

32:28.322 --> 32:29.322
(FREDERICO SPEAKING)

32:29.364 --> 32:30.364
So you lied.

32:31.575 --> 32:34.033
You did find something.

32:37.039 --> 32:38.530
Find anything else?

32:40.208 --> 32:41.208
Raphael...

32:48.967 --> 32:50.174
(SIGHING)

32:54.306 --> 32:55.922
Do you like rollercoasters?

32:56.975 --> 32:58.511
(GRUNTING)

33:00.312 --> 33:01.393
(CAR DOOR CLOSING)

33:02.272 --> 33:03.888
(RAPHAEL SOBBING)

33:14.785 --> 33:15.821
What a joke.

33:15.911 --> 33:17.652
Have some respect, old man.

33:17.746 --> 33:19.453
Raphael Fernandes!

33:19.665 --> 33:21.076
Can you hear me?

33:21.249 --> 33:22.831
Raphael, it's Father Julliard!

33:23.085 --> 33:24.872
I've come to take you home!

33:25.045 --> 33:26.045
Raphael!

33:26.171 --> 33:27.457
Answer me!

33:28.131 --> 33:29.417
You sons of bitches.

33:29.508 --> 33:31.249
You kidnapped that boy,

33:31.343 --> 33:33.084
and you're not going
to get away with it.

33:33.261 --> 33:34.593
God damn you!

33:34.763 --> 33:37.631
His name is Raphael Fernandes.
Do you hear me?

33:40.769 --> 33:42.476
(WHIMPERING)

34:04.835 --> 34:05.835
(GROANING)

34:07.796 --> 34:09.879
(PANTING)

34:15.137 --> 34:16.503
(SCREAMS ECHOING)

34:19.516 --> 34:20.757
(PANTING)

34:25.605 --> 34:26.857
(SCREAMING)

34:27.940 --> 34:29.306
(PANTING)

34:48.795 --> 34:50.661
Sorry, friends, we couldn't find him.
(SIGHING)

35:05.729 --> 35:07.391
He's probably dead by now.

35:29.294 --> 35:32.037
Don't waste your life fighting
battles that make you bitter

35:32.214 --> 35:33.705
or make you dead.

35:41.223 --> 35:44.057
Raphael Fernandes.
(SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)

35:54.444 --> 35:55.605
(RATO SIGHING)

35:55.695 --> 35:56.856
(RATO SPEAKING)

35:56.947 --> 35:59.155
He's with God now.

36:08.834 --> 36:09.995
(GRUNTING)

36:34.109 --> 36:36.476
Want to know
how José Angelo died?

36:42.659 --> 36:44.400
(WHISPERING IN PORTUGUESE)

36:49.499 --> 36:50.535
Are you praying?

36:55.130 --> 36:57.087
May God protect you.

36:58.049 --> 36:59.049
(CHUCKLING)

37:00.802 --> 37:01.838
Amen.

37:04.931 --> 37:05.931
Finish him.

37:06.308 --> 37:07.389
(CARLOS SPEAKING)

37:07.475 --> 37:10.218
What are you going
to tell Santos?

37:16.818 --> 37:19.026
(SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)
(CAR ENGINE STARTING)

37:32.876 --> 37:34.083
(BREATHING HEAVILY)

37:38.006 --> 37:39.006
(GUNSHOT)

37:40.008 --> 37:41.008
(CARLOS SPEAKING)

37:41.092 --> 37:42.674
You chickened out...

37:42.761 --> 37:43.761
(MAN SPEAKING)

37:43.845 --> 37:45.125
Santos can do
his own dirty work.

38:04.658 --> 38:05.658
(GASPS)

38:16.962 --> 38:18.578
(MAN YELLING)

38:26.179 --> 38:27.295
I'm not working anymore.

38:27.389 --> 38:28.721
(GARDO SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)

38:29.766 --> 38:30.766
(MAN SHOUTING)

38:30.850 --> 38:31.850
Help!

38:31.977 --> 38:34.139
There's a kid up
here on the road!

38:34.229 --> 38:36.061
(PEOPLE CLAMORING)

38:37.857 --> 38:39.018
Gardo!

38:51.371 --> 38:52.703
(SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)

38:54.249 --> 38:56.411
(INDISTINCT CHATTER)

39:03.341 --> 39:04.843
(COUGHING)

39:11.349 --> 39:12.385
(GROANING)

39:14.016 --> 39:15.496
(INHALING SHARPLY)
(JULLIARD SPEAKING)

39:15.520 --> 39:16.931
If you found the wallet

39:17.022 --> 39:18.022
(GASPS)

39:18.106 --> 39:21.270
the best plan is
to get out of trouble

39:21.401 --> 39:23.393
while you still have time.

39:26.197 --> 39:30.441
There's nothing
cowardly about it.

39:32.078 --> 39:35.037
In fact, it's the brave way out.

39:37.667 --> 39:40.410
If you give me the wallet

39:40.837 --> 39:41.837
I'll collect...

39:41.921 --> 39:43.128
(GASPS) Shh.

39:44.466 --> 39:46.082
The reward.

39:46.259 --> 39:48.967
Everyone's life

39:49.054 --> 39:51.046
will get a little bit better.

39:51.723 --> 39:53.840
A little bit better, is good.

39:54.684 --> 39:57.392
A little bit better is...

39:58.104 --> 40:00.517
a lot better than nothing.

40:02.650 --> 40:04.482
Okay? Hmm?

40:04.652 --> 40:06.109
(SPEAKING PORTUGUESE) <i>Sim.</i>

40:08.281 --> 40:09.783
Thank you, Father Julliard.

40:10.075 --> 40:12.317
You're welcome. Excuse me.

40:13.369 --> 40:14.655
(GROANING)

40:23.963 --> 40:24.963
(SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)

40:25.048 --> 40:27.290
You bringing trouble
to the community?

40:27.383 --> 40:28.999
No. (SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)

40:29.844 --> 40:31.927
So do you want to give up?

40:32.013 --> 40:34.096
Over my dead body.

40:34.474 --> 40:35.806
I want you to know...

40:37.310 --> 40:39.142
I'll follow you whatever.

40:39.729 --> 40:41.766
I just need a little rest first.

40:41.856 --> 40:43.188
(SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)

40:45.693 --> 40:47.855
If the cops didn't
kill me this time...

40:49.614 --> 40:51.321
they will next time.

40:52.283 --> 40:53.490
That was it.

40:54.452 --> 40:55.829
We had to go on.

40:57.288 --> 40:59.541
All we had was a name.

41:00.416 --> 41:01.702
So tell me this...

41:02.335 --> 41:04.042
how could we get into a prison?

41:05.713 --> 41:07.249
We needed a plan.

41:07.924 --> 41:09.711
We needed a miracle.

41:10.385 --> 41:11.385
That too.

41:19.227 --> 41:20.434
RATO: Psst. More.

41:20.645 --> 41:21.645
(SLAMMING)

41:25.483 --> 41:27.019
Boys, what are you doing here?

41:27.110 --> 41:28.726
We told you to sleep
at the church.

41:30.155 --> 41:31.236
Hmm?

41:31.739 --> 41:33.355
(SPEAKING PORTUGUESE) No.

41:34.159 --> 41:37.243
GARDO: Miss Olive.
Miss Olivia, we need you.

41:38.705 --> 41:40.241
We need favor.

41:40.582 --> 41:42.619
Police... will...

41:44.210 --> 41:45.667
kill... him.

41:45.920 --> 41:47.661
GARDO: Raphael's danger,
Miss Olivia.

41:48.089 --> 41:49.250
Help. Boys...

41:49.340 --> 41:51.252
Raphael needs a liar.

41:51.467 --> 41:53.333
OLMA: He needs a liar?
GARDO: Yeah.

41:53.595 --> 41:54.756
I don't understand.

41:54.971 --> 41:56.803
Show it to her.

41:56.931 --> 41:57.967
Justice.

41:58.558 --> 42:00.140
A lawyer. He needs a lawyer.

42:00.476 --> 42:01.762
GARDO: Yes. A lawyer.

42:01.895 --> 42:03.727
My grandfather is very lawyer.

42:04.772 --> 42:07.685
Your grandfather is a lawyer.
Yeah, he can help Raphael.

42:11.863 --> 42:13.024
Really?

42:13.114 --> 42:14.150
(SPEAKING IN PORTUGUESE)

42:14.240 --> 42:15.572
Where's your grandfather?

42:16.784 --> 42:20.118
My grandfather is prisoner.

42:20.788 --> 42:21.949
Yeah. Prison.

42:22.040 --> 42:23.201
(COUGHING)

42:23.958 --> 42:25.039
(SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)

42:25.126 --> 42:26.537
Why do you...

42:27.253 --> 42:29.290
Why do you need me?

42:30.340 --> 42:32.548
You are an American.

42:34.427 --> 42:36.760
You white. RATO: You white.

42:37.180 --> 42:38.637
You black.

42:38.806 --> 42:40.138
You white.

42:40.642 --> 42:41.758
White.

42:42.685 --> 42:45.143
I look poor.

42:45.521 --> 42:47.478
My brother.

42:48.358 --> 42:49.998
OLMA: These are your brothers?
RATO: Yes.

42:50.360 --> 42:52.397
You my mother.

42:54.322 --> 42:55.483
GARDO: Miss Olive,

42:56.324 --> 42:57.656
we need you.

42:58.910 --> 43:00.321
(GARDO READING PORTUGUESE)

43:03.039 --> 43:04.951
Gardo. Gardo.

43:07.210 --> 43:08.917
I remembered something.

43:09.003 --> 43:10.505
(SPEAKING PORTUGUESE) (GROANING)

43:11.881 --> 43:15.090
The cops were talking
about a guy called Santos.

43:15.176 --> 43:16.383
(SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)

43:17.095 --> 43:19.087
I think he wants the letter.

43:19.555 --> 43:20.887
(SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)

43:21.182 --> 43:22.923
Hey, I know Santos...

43:23.017 --> 43:24.017
(SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)

43:24.352 --> 43:25.684
He's that politician.

43:26.354 --> 43:28.562
The fat bastard
wants to be Mayor.

43:29.107 --> 43:30.268
Do you know where he lives?

43:30.441 --> 43:33.525
Where all the fat bastards
live - near the beach.

43:35.613 --> 43:37.320
I can take you there.

43:37.573 --> 43:41.442
What did Santos want with me?
Why did he want me dead?

43:41.536 --> 43:43.323
I've done nothing to him.

43:44.497 --> 43:45.908
Doesn't make sense.

43:46.291 --> 43:48.203
I just wanted to
go to the beach.

44:19.198 --> 44:20.359
(KISSING SOUND)

44:22.076 --> 44:23.112
Hey, hot stuff!

44:23.202 --> 44:24.283
(BOTH LAUGHING)

44:33.171 --> 44:34.787
I've never been to the beach.

44:35.506 --> 44:38.419
I lived on the beach.
I was born there.

44:39.385 --> 44:40.421
What was it like?

44:40.678 --> 44:42.294
It was beautiful.

44:42.388 --> 44:43.890
Far away from here...

44:43.973 --> 44:46.431
Perfect water.
You can see the fish.

44:47.060 --> 44:48.551
You never go hungry there.

44:49.020 --> 44:50.477
Make money fishing.

44:52.982 --> 44:54.439
Life there is fair.

44:55.276 --> 44:58.019
I'm going to move back -
you should come with me.

45:03.451 --> 45:04.987
Sounds great.

45:18.424 --> 45:19.585
(PRISON GUARD SPEAKING)

45:19.675 --> 45:23.339
If you don't have a pass,
you don't get in...

45:25.306 --> 45:26.968
(INDISTINCT CHATTER)

45:27.266 --> 45:28.427
(DOG BARKING)

45:30.812 --> 45:32.019
(GARDO SPEAKING)

45:32.105 --> 45:34.188
We have to wait in line.

45:34.273 --> 45:35.980
(WOMAN SHOUTING)

45:36.401 --> 45:37.687
(SIREN WAILING)

45:40.613 --> 45:42.605
(BOTH SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)

45:55.670 --> 45:56.786
(SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)

45:57.630 --> 45:58.666
(GRUNTING)

46:06.013 --> 46:07.094
(SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)

46:07.932 --> 46:09.639
Are you sure
this is Santos' house?

46:09.725 --> 46:11.717
Yeah, I saw it on TV.

46:14.689 --> 46:16.100
(GRUNTING) (DOG BARKING)

46:16.190 --> 46:17.351
(RAPHAEL GRUNTING)

46:20.445 --> 46:21.856
(SPEAKING PORTUGUESE) (GROWLING)

46:22.864 --> 46:24.321
MAN: You see,

46:24.407 --> 46:27.571
visits for Mr. Clemente
are usually restricted.

46:28.744 --> 46:31.236
So, I'm sorry.

46:31.372 --> 46:32.408
(BARKING)

46:33.291 --> 46:35.078
(BARKING) (SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)

46:36.210 --> 46:37.246
What's going on here?

46:37.336 --> 46:39.123
Just picking fruit.

46:39.213 --> 46:40.249
(SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)

46:40.590 --> 46:42.172
Are you armed?

46:42.300 --> 46:43.461
No. No.

46:46.762 --> 46:47.969
But this is his grandson,

46:48.055 --> 46:51.219
so isn't there something
we can do to fix that?

46:51.309 --> 46:52.766
His grandson?

46:53.478 --> 46:54.685
OLMA: Yeah.

46:56.939 --> 46:58.726
Well, (EXHALING)

46:58.816 --> 47:02.526
I can make an arrangement
if you want, but, um...

47:02.737 --> 47:05.354
OLMA: Yeah. You have to help.

47:07.158 --> 47:09.241
You're crazy, jumping
onto private property.

47:09.368 --> 47:10.904
(DOG BARKING)

47:11.120 --> 47:12.452
(WOMAN SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)

47:13.498 --> 47:14.579
Scram.

47:15.416 --> 47:16.416
(WOMAN SPEAKING)

47:16.709 --> 47:19.577
Shut those dogs up right now!

47:19.879 --> 47:21.495
Do I have to do
everything myself?

47:21.839 --> 47:23.296
(SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)

47:25.092 --> 47:26.549
(MAN HUMMING)

47:31.265 --> 47:33.302
(SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)

47:34.977 --> 47:36.138
(SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)

47:37.688 --> 47:38.688
Crazy woman.

47:39.190 --> 47:40.397
Get down.

47:40.733 --> 47:43.476
If Mrs Santos catches you,
she'll kill you.

47:43.819 --> 47:46.277
You picked a terrible
time to drop in.

47:46.614 --> 47:47.695
What's going on?

47:48.950 --> 47:50.532
(CLAMORING)

47:51.953 --> 47:53.945
(INDISTINCT SHOUTING)

48:04.757 --> 48:06.373
(SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)

48:17.603 --> 48:19.310
(SHOUTING CONTINUING)

48:20.982 --> 48:22.314
(CELL DOOR CLOSING)

48:28.155 --> 48:29.441
(DOOR OPENING)

48:38.833 --> 48:39.914
Good morning.

48:40.501 --> 48:41.537
(GREETING IN PORTUGUESE)

48:42.336 --> 48:43.668
You speak my language?

48:44.005 --> 48:45.337
A little.

48:45.715 --> 48:47.331
Thanks for the visit.

48:47.842 --> 48:50.835
I hope it wasn't too traumatic.

48:51.304 --> 48:52.511
(SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)

48:53.431 --> 48:54.592
What's your name, kid?

48:54.682 --> 48:55.638
Gardo. (SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)

48:55.725 --> 48:57.432
Gardo. Hmm.

48:59.020 --> 49:01.103
Why do you come to visit me?

49:01.522 --> 49:03.024
Expensive, isn't it?

49:05.776 --> 49:08.189
Well, Gardo, here

49:09.780 --> 49:11.612
really wanted to talk to you.

49:12.575 --> 49:13.782
Right, Gardo?

49:13.951 --> 49:15.112
You wanted to see him.

49:15.328 --> 49:17.615
And what he's got to do with me?

49:19.665 --> 49:23.158
Well, he said that you were family.
(CHUCKLING)

49:23.711 --> 49:24.918
He said?

49:25.546 --> 49:27.048
And you believe it.

49:27.381 --> 49:28.497
(BREATHING DEEPLY)

49:29.050 --> 49:30.382
Who gave you my name?

49:32.386 --> 49:33.763
What's your scam, punk?

49:35.264 --> 49:36.505
Okay.

49:36.974 --> 49:38.715
I think we should go.

49:44.607 --> 49:45.688
(MAN SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)

49:45.775 --> 49:47.357
What's with all the security?

49:47.443 --> 49:49.605
Something important
was stolen from the boss.

49:49.695 --> 49:51.027
Was it a wallet?

49:51.113 --> 49:52.615
He wishes.

49:53.282 --> 49:55.820
You think you can fit
10 million in a wallet?

49:57.745 --> 49:58.745
Who stole it?

49:58.788 --> 49:59.788
(THIAGO SPEAKING)

49:59.872 --> 50:01.033
His name is José Angelo.

50:01.540 --> 50:03.076
The boss's right-hand man.

50:03.167 --> 50:04.829
Fucking destroyed him.

50:05.628 --> 50:06.744
(EXHALING AND GROANING)

50:08.631 --> 50:09.917
Can you give me a hand?

50:10.007 --> 50:11.509
I saved your ass.

50:12.051 --> 50:14.759
Go get the bags on the lawn.

50:15.096 --> 50:16.928
(COUGHING) Hello? <i>Por favor.</i>

50:17.848 --> 50:19.009
(SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)

50:20.476 --> 50:21.887
I have a message for you.

50:25.439 --> 50:27.772
He says he has a message.

50:28.192 --> 50:29.353
What message?

50:30.027 --> 50:31.768
From José Angelo.

50:39.370 --> 50:42.454
José Angelo? Yeah.
(SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)

50:42.623 --> 50:45.411
"Fear no more,
it is accomplished."

50:45.626 --> 50:46.833
How do you know this?

50:46.919 --> 50:49.127
It was in a letter we found,
he wrote to you.

50:50.965 --> 50:52.081
What did he say?

50:52.133 --> 50:53.454
Are you talking about Raphael?
No.

50:53.467 --> 50:55.584
José Angelo is my nephew.

50:57.596 --> 50:58.882
Do you have the letter here?

50:59.473 --> 51:00.975
No - it's here.

51:01.642 --> 51:03.053
I memorised it.

51:03.310 --> 51:04.391
(SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)

51:08.482 --> 51:09.482
Tell me.

51:09.608 --> 51:11.110
It read like this:

51:12.653 --> 51:14.315
Dear Sir,

51:15.072 --> 51:19.487
I haven't written in a long time,
but I think of you always.

51:20.286 --> 51:22.824
I have something
important to tell you,

51:23.497 --> 51:26.160
in the words
you once spoke to me:

51:27.251 --> 51:30.164
<i>"Fear no more,</i>
<i>it is accomplished."</i>

51:30.379 --> 51:31.379
(JOSÉ SPEAKING)

51:31.464 --> 51:36.175
Soon, the devil who put you
behind bars will be chained,

51:37.011 --> 51:41.176
his corruption and
lies all exposed.

51:42.516 --> 51:45.350
Your struggle was not in vain.

51:47.354 --> 51:48.354
I promise.

51:49.607 --> 51:55.353
Santos will be finished and, God willing,
he is only the first domino to fall.

51:57.323 --> 52:02.284
Your fight against the corruption that
destroyed our dream for justice goes on.

52:02.369 --> 52:06.283
Even now people flood the streets, fanning
the flames of hope that you helped ignite.

52:06.373 --> 52:07.454
(MOUTHING)

52:08.667 --> 52:10.044
Change is coming.

52:11.712 --> 52:13.829
But with joy comes sorrow.

52:14.465 --> 52:18.960
If you are reading this,
it means I've been taken.

52:20.054 --> 52:21.886
And they will not be merciful.

52:23.057 --> 52:29.725
But the dream you passed to me
is passed to new generations.

52:32.733 --> 52:38.195
I'm sorry for being a burden - you
have suffered so much already.

52:39.740 --> 52:45.077
This letter has the secret -
it seals our enemy's fate.

52:48.082 --> 52:49.994
Do what must be done.

52:51.877 --> 52:56.747
I pray for you,
and for my daughter Pia

52:57.174 --> 52:59.666
and for all who
fight for our people.

53:02.596 --> 53:03.928
(SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)

53:11.438 --> 53:13.145
(CLEMENTE SOBBING)

53:18.112 --> 53:19.694
(WHISPERING) Hallelujah.

53:30.416 --> 53:31.623
How did José do it?

53:31.709 --> 53:32.950
You're nosy.

53:33.043 --> 53:34.454
Just tell us.

53:37.423 --> 53:40.507
Ok, this is the fun part.

53:40.593 --> 53:42.334
You won't believe it.

53:43.012 --> 53:46.380
As I told you, he was the
boss's right-hand man...

53:46.891 --> 53:48.302
(WHISPERING IN PORTUGUESE)

53:48.809 --> 53:50.095
(SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)

53:52.479 --> 53:54.311
(INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS)

53:56.650 --> 53:58.232
How are you, Congressman?

53:58.402 --> 53:59.938
Good, everyone's here.

54:00.988 --> 54:01.988
(ANTONIO SPEAKING)

54:02.072 --> 54:03.358
Such generosity.

54:04.366 --> 54:06.403
Ok, let's make me Mayor.

54:06.911 --> 54:07.911
(ANTONIO SPEAKING)

54:07.995 --> 54:09.987
I love businessmen.

54:10.080 --> 54:12.697
They've covered
all my election costs.

54:13.500 --> 54:16.413
Maybe I'll even throw
the police a few bucks...

54:17.212 --> 54:18.714
No computer.

54:19.381 --> 54:21.919
Everything in my little book.

54:23.469 --> 54:25.005
Keep it safe.

54:26.513 --> 54:27.594
Ze.

54:30.976 --> 54:33.935
Thank you - for everything.

54:38.025 --> 54:40.062
You're welcome, boss.

54:40.152 --> 54:41.188
(SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)

54:42.696 --> 54:43.857
(BEEPING)

54:52.081 --> 54:54.448
Safe trip, Congressman.

55:17.314 --> 55:18.314
(ANGELINA SPEAKING)

55:18.399 --> 55:20.311
Oh my God - all this water.

55:22.111 --> 55:24.478
The freezer's broken again.

55:25.197 --> 55:27.189
This one's a lost cause.

55:28.409 --> 55:30.901
Let's chuck it out
and get a new one.

55:31.203 --> 55:32.364
(WATER SPLASHING)

55:33.956 --> 55:35.072
(BEEPING)

55:49.346 --> 55:50.382
(EXHALING)

55:50.889 --> 55:52.096
(CHUCKLING)

56:00.774 --> 56:01.774
(GRUNTING)

56:03.861 --> 56:05.773
What are you doing
with the trash?

56:06.488 --> 56:07.945
Doing your job...

56:08.323 --> 56:11.612
How long is this fridge
staying here?

56:12.327 --> 56:14.614
It'll be picked up
in the morning.

56:41.440 --> 56:44.148
R$40 to take the
fridge to my house?

56:45.110 --> 56:46.442
Is it far?

56:47.071 --> 56:49.108
I'll go with you.

56:49.698 --> 56:52.566
R$20 more to carry it upstairs.

56:52.785 --> 56:53.785
Okay.

56:54.995 --> 56:56.611
<i>Obrigado.</i> (CUPS CLINKING)

57:03.879 --> 57:06.417
José, where you
taking that junk?

57:06.507 --> 57:07.748
Home.

57:08.425 --> 57:10.417
I'll fill it with ice-cream
for my daughter.

57:10.511 --> 57:11.511
Ah.

57:13.180 --> 57:14.180
(SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)

57:37.454 --> 57:39.446
Was there something else?

57:40.833 --> 57:42.040
There was a photo...

57:42.334 --> 57:43.996
A photo with numbers.

57:44.670 --> 57:46.662
Marco, I need my bible!

57:50.342 --> 57:51.342
Marco.

57:51.426 --> 57:52.426
Yes, Mr. Clemente?

57:52.511 --> 57:54.252
I need my bible.

57:54.930 --> 57:56.922
The visit is over.

57:57.891 --> 57:59.883
She's come to help me.

57:59.977 --> 58:01.184
The boy has a message.

58:01.270 --> 58:02.727
I need to reply.

58:03.730 --> 58:06.894
If I bring the bible now
things could get ugly for us.

58:07.317 --> 58:10.936
Ask them to come back tomorrow.
I'll give it to them then.

58:12.114 --> 58:13.696
It's too dangerous.

58:17.786 --> 58:19.948
He can't help us now.

58:22.749 --> 58:25.002
Come back tomorrow. Find him.

58:25.919 --> 58:27.581
He will give you the bible.

58:28.130 --> 58:30.588
The bible has a code.

58:31.258 --> 58:34.922
Page, chapter, and verse.

58:35.179 --> 58:38.672
It's simple.
You'll understand easily.

58:40.434 --> 58:42.016
(SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)

58:43.687 --> 58:45.599
Two identical bibles...

58:45.689 --> 58:47.396
It's how we sent messages.

58:48.609 --> 58:49.609
Use mine...

58:49.693 --> 58:51.980
to find what José has hidden.

58:52.863 --> 58:54.274
You have to find it.

58:55.073 --> 58:56.325
Help us.

59:00.287 --> 59:01.448
(SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)

59:05.292 --> 59:06.373
(HUMMING)

59:10.505 --> 59:11.586
Thank you.

59:14.551 --> 59:16.213
We won't see each other again.

59:21.141 --> 59:23.133
But we'll be together forever.

59:26.897 --> 59:28.138
(SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)

59:32.527 --> 59:34.234
I spoke to Marco...

59:35.489 --> 59:38.482
He wants R$1000 for the bible.

59:38.617 --> 59:39.778
(CLICKS TONGUE)

59:39.952 --> 59:40.952
(SIGHING)

59:49.503 --> 59:50.835
I think that's the code.

59:51.004 --> 59:52.836
He says the code.

59:53.382 --> 59:54.839
From the bible? Yes.

59:55.008 --> 59:56.465
Olivia. Yeah.

59:56.593 --> 59:57.754
The letter?

59:59.888 --> 01:00:01.174
Of course. <i>Obrigado.</i>

01:00:08.730 --> 01:00:10.983
Why are you doing all this?

01:00:16.697 --> 01:00:18.188
Because it's right.

01:00:20.367 --> 01:00:21.949
(SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)

01:00:22.869 --> 01:00:25.282
We need money.
We need the bible.

01:00:25.372 --> 01:00:27.910
Marco wants money for the bible.

01:00:28.750 --> 01:00:30.457
Of course he does.
RATO: Raphael.

01:00:31.420 --> 01:00:33.082
What do you think?

01:00:33.338 --> 01:00:35.204
I think she won't
give us the money.

01:00:35.299 --> 01:00:37.211
Then we're screwed.

01:00:37.467 --> 01:00:38.674
Chill out, man.

01:00:38.760 --> 01:00:40.262
Getting the money is easy.

01:00:40.679 --> 01:00:42.341
We got her to the prison...

01:00:42.431 --> 01:00:44.388
Money will be easy.

01:00:45.350 --> 01:00:46.636
Money is never easy.

01:00:46.727 --> 01:00:47.727
(CAMERA CHIMING)

01:00:51.940 --> 01:00:53.772
Do you boys want
to try something?

01:00:53.859 --> 01:00:55.976
You want to make a video?

01:00:56.486 --> 01:00:58.899
I think she wants to
make a porno.

01:00:59.364 --> 01:01:00.696
Do you want to make a film?

01:01:00.782 --> 01:01:03.274
You can tell me the story from
the beginning and I'll film it.

01:01:03.493 --> 01:01:06.861
Sorry, she wants to make a
video - but not a porno.

01:01:06.955 --> 01:01:10.995
We tell the wallet story and
she'll ask questions. Cool?

01:01:11.418 --> 01:01:13.330
Do I have to
take my clothes off?

01:01:13.462 --> 01:01:15.670
Boys? (SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)

01:01:15.964 --> 01:01:17.125
(SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)

01:01:17.591 --> 01:01:19.583
<i>Sim.</i> Yes.

01:01:20.886 --> 01:01:21.886
Let's go.

01:01:22.304 --> 01:01:23.761
(CHUCKLING) Okay, let's go.

01:01:25.015 --> 01:01:26.096
Let's do it over there.

01:01:26.308 --> 01:01:27.958
OLMA: Okay, tell me your story.

01:01:29.895 --> 01:01:31.011
(CHUCKLING)

01:01:31.980 --> 01:01:33.812
My name is Raphael.

01:01:35.442 --> 01:01:37.434
I am 14.

01:01:40.280 --> 01:01:43.864
I work in the trash.

01:01:44.951 --> 01:01:46.283
The police

01:01:48.330 --> 01:01:49.787
hit me.

01:01:52.292 --> 01:01:54.284
I don't like police.

01:01:55.796 --> 01:01:57.207
(CELL PHONE RINGING)

01:01:59.925 --> 01:02:00.925
(CELL PHONE BEEPING)

01:02:00.967 --> 01:02:01.967
(ANTONIO SPEAKING)

01:02:02.052 --> 01:02:05.261
While you were taking children
on fairground rides...

01:02:05.347 --> 01:02:07.805
a gringa and some trash boy
were with Clemente.

01:02:07.891 --> 01:02:08.972
A boy of what age?

01:02:09.059 --> 01:02:09.845
Listen to me...

01:02:09.935 --> 01:02:11.551
I want my money.

01:02:11.645 --> 01:02:13.181
I want my book.

01:02:13.480 --> 01:02:16.143
I want you to tear
that place down.

01:02:16.525 --> 01:02:18.266
Tear the dump apart.

01:02:18.360 --> 01:02:20.147
Shut it down!

01:02:20.237 --> 01:02:21.237
(RATO SPEAKING)

01:02:21.321 --> 01:02:22.778
Santos acts like
a nice guy on TV...

01:02:23.407 --> 01:02:27.117
but leaves us without
schools and hospitals.

01:02:27.244 --> 01:02:28.906
(CAR APPROACHING)
(SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)

01:02:31.498 --> 01:02:32.614
(SIREN WAILING)

01:02:32.999 --> 01:02:34.206
(SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)

01:02:37.003 --> 01:02:38.164
(DOOR SLAMS OPEN)

01:02:38.463 --> 01:02:40.329
(POLICE SPEAKING INDISTINCTLY)
(GASPS)

01:02:49.641 --> 01:02:50.641
(FREDERICO SPEAKING)

01:02:50.684 --> 01:02:51.684
Leave.

01:03:03.029 --> 01:03:04.190
(DOOR CLOSING)

01:03:10.078 --> 01:03:11.194
(GASPS)

01:03:34.978 --> 01:03:36.890
You're working here.
(CLICKS TONGUE)

01:03:38.940 --> 01:03:40.056
So,

01:03:41.943 --> 01:03:43.900
you need a special
stamp for that.

01:03:44.529 --> 01:03:46.521
(BREATHING DEEPLY)

01:03:50.869 --> 01:03:51.985
(CHUCKLING)

01:04:10.597 --> 01:04:12.714
I don't know if you
are the kind of person

01:04:12.807 --> 01:04:15.766
who takes criticism well,
but I got to tell you,

01:04:16.853 --> 01:04:19.516
smuggling a minor into prison...
(CLICKS TONGUE)

01:04:19.648 --> 01:04:22.356
is not exactly a bright idea.

01:04:23.527 --> 01:04:24.984
And bribing people...

01:04:26.738 --> 01:04:29.230
I don't know in your
country, but here,

01:04:29.324 --> 01:04:32.317
it's a huge, huge offense.

01:04:39.584 --> 01:04:41.450
You need to come with me.

01:04:42.921 --> 01:04:45.129
(SIREN WAILING)
(INDISTINCT CHATTER)

01:04:54.474 --> 01:04:55.715
(GASPS)

01:04:57.852 --> 01:04:59.434
(SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)

01:05:02.691 --> 01:05:03.691
(RATO SPEAKING)

01:05:03.775 --> 01:05:05.357
There's something
going on at the dump.

01:05:08.154 --> 01:05:09.190
Can you see anything?

01:05:09.281 --> 01:05:10.613
Hold on...

01:05:10.782 --> 01:05:11.863
(FIRE CRACKLING)

01:05:12.325 --> 01:05:13.577
Oh God!

01:05:13.660 --> 01:05:14.741
(SPEAKING PORTUGUESE)

01:05:15.495 --> 01:05:16.906
It's all gone.

01:05:18.164 --> 01:05:20.417
(MAN SHOUTING IN PORTUGUESE)

01:05:22.836 --> 01:05:24.668
(FIRE CRACKLING)

01:05:28.675 --> 01:05:30.917
(SIREN WAILING)
(PEOPLE SHOUTING)

01:05:53.658 --> 01:05:54.658
(RATO SPEAKING)

01:05:54.701 --> 01:05:57.068
We've got to go...
the police did this.

01:05:57.162 --> 01:05:59.119
They'll find us.

01:06:03.335 --> 01:06:05.122
What did we do?

01:06:06.087 --> 01:06:07.919
I don't know.

01:06:12.677 --> 01:06:15.340
Let's get that bible, come on.

01:06:32.405 --> 01:06:33.405
(GARDO PRAYING)

01:06:33.490 --> 01:06:34.947
Our Father who art in heaven.

01:06:35.408 --> 01:06:36.910
